{"tid":611453,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(超級準)想買料既入一入嚟 上樓不是夢","createTime":"2018-03-31T04:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T05:09:44.000Z","uid":15440,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe739dac3b55ffecdbcbae7096821c84d52ce296","tid":611453,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒未啊仆街？有料仲洗問你攞錢啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你地想買料停一停，諗一諗<br />\n<br />\n一個有料既人會唔會貪你一萬幾千？醒下啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將買料既錢留返去同屋企人飲茶好過啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好再信乜野收費，要pm先有料，要幫佢宣傳先有毒料既人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>坊間有好多交流群係唔收錢<br />\n坊間有好多交流群係唔收錢<br />\n坊間有好多交流群係唔收錢<br />\n坊間有好多交流群係唔收錢</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我牛屎佬打擊賣料同時創立左 4000人賭波gp <br />\n入面無人賣料 無人宣傳 無人事後飛 <br />\n<br />\n高手雲集，重點係免費啊 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://T.me/ballgp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fballgp&d=4%2BrRIQTk%2BJ4g0iBcleXrgSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1120ffed\" target=\"_blank\">http://T.me/ballgp</a>"},{"pid":"d655b72af17f72f81112ed93b0150fde1ce9b788","tid":611453,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eff7029d27ca72dc1a6c441fbe9ffd8869b46c5","tid":611453,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"b24526085134f6a272b785deee45a39d18ffbddb","tid":611453,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eff7029d27ca72dc1a6c441fbe9ffd8869b46c5","tid":611453,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:33:04.000Z","msg":"G持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6a96685e2942d9fd7967e4cb8558325d044038","tid":611453,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"